00:34:58,120 --> 00:34:59,319
Hindi na kailangan.

494
00:34:59,320 --> 00:35:01,320
Ngayon, ipagluluto kita.

495
00:35:01,840 --> 00:35:03,560
Nanay, huwag kang mag-abala.

496
00:35:03,960 --> 00:35:04,960
Magpahinga ka na.

497
00:35:05,400 --> 00:35:08,279
Ngayon, sobrang energetic ang pakiramdam ko.

498
00:35:08,280 --> 00:35:09,720
Nasa mabuting kalagayan ako.

499
00:35:09,800 --> 00:35:10,800
Sige.

500
00:35:13,200 --> 00:35:14,200
Pumunta ka na sa kwarto mo at magpahinga.

501
00:35:14,240 --> 00:35:15,279
Hindi na kailangan, Mom.

502
00:35:15,280 --> 00:35:17,200
- Mananatili ako dito kasama mo.
- Okay.

503
00:35:28,800 --> 00:35:29,920
Tingnan mo.

504
00:35:30,120 --> 00:35:32,520
Napakaganda ng paglaki ng bulaklak na ito.

505
00:35:58,840 --> 00:35:59,840
Dito, Nanay.

506
00:35:59,920 --> 00:36:00,920
Kumain ka ng sopas.

507
00:36:12,160 --> 00:36:13,160
Da Qiong.

508
00:36:13,920 --> 00:36:15,240
kailan ka...

509
00:36:15,960 --> 00:36:17,640
kukuha ba ako ng manugang?

510
00:36:23,160 --> 00:36:24,160
Malapit na.

511
00:36:36,880 --> 00:36:38,600
Masyadong abala si Xiao Chi nitong mga nakaraang araw.

512
00:36:41,400 --> 00:36:42,400
Siya...

513
00:36:42,960 --> 00:36:44,040
ay medyo abala.

514
00:36:47,640 --> 00:36:49,400
Si Xiao Chi ay isang mabuting tao.

515
00:36:54,840 --> 00:36:55,880
Mabait siya.

516
00:37:21,920 --> 00:37:22,920
Nanay.

517
00:37:23,840 --> 00:37:24,840
Nanay.

518
00:37:26,440 --> 00:37:27,440
Tara kain na tayo.

519
00:37:27,480 --> 00:37:28,480
Okay.

520
00:38:12,440 --> 00:38:13,440
Nanay.

521
00:38:13,920 --> 00:38:15,200
Bakit dito ka natutulog?

522
00:38:21,880 --> 00:38:23,920
Tara na.
Tutulungan kita sa kwarto mo.

523
00:39:12,160 --> 00:39:13,160
Nanay.

524
00:39:16,360 --> 00:39:17,880
tignan mo.

525
00:39:20,600 --> 00:39:21,600
Summer na...

526
00:39:22,160 --> 00:39:23,560
at sa bakuran ka natutulog.

527
00:39:24,240 --> 00:39:25,600
Paano kung taglamig na?

528
00:39:28,400 --> 00:39:30,080
Hindi ako makakasama sa lahat ng oras.

529
00:39:30,920 --> 00:39:32,760
Kung ikaw ay may sakit ng ulo o lagnat,

530
00:39:34,640 --> 00:39:35,920
Hindi kita kayang alagaan.

531
00:39:39,840 --> 00:39:40,840
Nanay.

532
00:39:42,480 --> 00:39:44,600
Bakit hindi ako bumili ng malapit na bahay?

533
00:39:48,120 --> 00:39:49,680
Maaari kang lumipat sa akin ...

534
00:39:50,600 --> 00:39:51,840
at kaya kitang alagaan.

535
00:40:06,560 --> 00:40:08,440
Lagi mong sinasabi na isang pagpapala
ang magdusa ng mga pagkalugi.

536
00:40:09,720 --> 00:40:11,480
Masarap mamuhay ng matiwasay.

537
00:40:14,200 --> 00:40:15,200
Nanay.

538
00:40:16,640 --> 00:40:18,360
Actually, hindi ko sinabi sayo...

539
00:40:19,800 --> 00:40:21,320
na nagsimula ako ng isang kumpanya.

540
00:40:23,720 --> 00:40:25,160
Hindi ko ginustong mag-alala ka sa akin,

541
00:40:30,400 --> 00:40:31,640
kaya hindi ako naglakas loob na sabihin sayo.

542
00:40:38,920 --> 00:40:40,120
Hindi mo naman ako masisisi diba?

543
00:40:48,680 --> 00:40:50,280
Actually, karapat dapat akong sisihin.

544
00:40:51,640 --> 00:40:52,640
unfilial ako.

545
00:40:54,720 --> 00:40:56,280
Hindi kita nabigyan ng magandang buhay.

546
00:41:36,560 --> 00:41:37,560
Nanay.

547
00:41:39,960 --> 00:41:40,960
pasensya na po.

548
00:41:43,560 --> 00:41:44,720
Nagsinungaling na naman ako sayo.

549
00:41:47,120 --> 00:41:48,200
hindi ko akalain...

550
00:41:49,880 --> 00:41:51,960
Magkakaroon ako ng asawa
sa buhay na ito.

551
00:42:15,560 --> 00:42:16,560
Nanay.

552
00:42:19,920 --> 00:42:20,920
Nanay.

553
00:42:22,680 --> 00:42:23,800
huwag kang pumunta.

554
00:42:34,080 --> 00:42:35,080
Nanay.
